<p>If you can't use the online service, you can apply by post by printing and filling in the <a href="/government/publications/carers-allowance-claim-form">DS700 form</a> or <a href="/government/publications/carers-allowance-claim-form">DS700SP form</a> if you get a State Pension.</p><p>Send your application to the <a href="/carers-allowance-unit">Carer’s Allowance Unit</a> – you can also contact them to get a printed form.</p>

